title: 11/02: Start or Sit (NFC); Nick Mullens!; Beat the Waiver Wire (Fantasy Football Podcast)
description:
Who is this Nick Mullens guy and is he going to be worth streaming next week? We start with a recap of the OAK-SF game and wonder if anyone on these teams other than the TEs has rest of season value ... News and notes (10:50) from around the NFL. What do we do if Sony Michel or Dalvin Cooks plays, or if Melvin Gordon does not? Then we've got the Startometer (14:30), a few emails (17:25) and Beat the Waiver Wire (22:24) ... ARI-WAS (25:50), LAR-NO (34:01), DET-MIN (43:08), TB-CAR (50:18), LAC-SEA (55:05), TEN-DAL (58:58) ... Your emails at fantasyfootball@cbsi.com
